modelchain is a universal, zero-runtime-dependency library and CLI for
intelligent, measurable LLM routing across OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, and any
OpenAI-compatible HTTP endpoint, with native streaming, native tool calling,
and a Vercel AI SDK adapter.

